---
title: Tex-Mex Taco Burgers with Guacamole & a Side of Tortilla Chips
description: The HF burger lab is open and they’ve invented a crowd-pleasing mashup of ground beef, Tex-Mex seasoning, and scallions. Griddle to juicy perfection, then tuck into fluffy toasted potato buns spread with guacamole and layered with sliced tomato. Serve blue tortilla chips on the side to make burger night an instant fiesta.
